<Layout title="About Us | Te Kete Ako">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">About Te Kete Ako</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2 mb-8">Te Kete Ako is a project dedicated to providing high-quality, culturally responsive learning resources for students at Mangakōtukutuku College. Our mission is to support diverse learners by offering a rich bank of accessible educational content, designed with the unique needs and cultural context of our kura in mind.</p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2 mb-8">This platform is built and maintained through an innovative automated workflow, leveraging AI agents to enhance content creation, organization, and delivery. We believe in the power of technology to support education and empower our students and kaiako.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Our Vision</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2">To create a dynamic and evolving digital learning environment that reflects the rich cultural tapestry of Mangakōtukutuku College, fostering a love for learning and preparing students for a future where digital literacy and critical thinking are paramount.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>